{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.029.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Tsiklag pill\u00e9e et incendi\u00e9e par les Amal\u00e9cites. Les Amal\u00e9cites battus par David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-31: cf. (1 Ch 12:19-22. Ge 14:11-16.) Jos 22:8. J\u00e9 41:11, etc. (Ro 15:1-7.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque David arriva le troisi\u00e8me jour \u00e0 Tsiklag avec ses gens, les Amal\u00e9cites avaient fait une invasion dans le midi et \u00e0 Tsiklag. Ils avaient d\u00e9truit et br\u00fbl\u00e9 Tsiklag,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2","name":"1 Samuel 30:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.29.11","name":"1 Samuel 29:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.29.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>apr\u00e8s avoir fait prisonniers les femmes et tous ceux qui s\u2019y trouvaient, petits et grands. Ils n\u2019avaient tu\u00e9 personne, mais ils avaient tout emmen\u00e9 et s\u2019\u00e9taient remis en route.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3","name":"1 Samuel 30:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.1","name":"1 Samuel 30:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>David et ses gens arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 la ville, et voici, elle \u00e9tait br\u00fbl\u00e9e; et leurs femmes, leurs fils et leurs filles, \u00e9taient emmen\u00e9s captifs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4","name":"1 Samuel 30:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2","name":"1 Samuel 30:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Alors David et le peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui \u00e9lev\u00e8rent la voix et pleur\u00e8rent jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019ils n\u2019eussent plus la force de pleurer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5","name":"1 Samuel 30:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3","name":"1 Samuel 30:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les deux femmes de David avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 emmen\u00e9es, Achinoam de Jizreel, et Abiga\u00efl de Carmel, femme de Nabal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6","name":"1 Samuel 30:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4","name":"1 Samuel 30:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>David fut dans une grande angoisse, car le peuple parlait de le lapider, parce que tous avaient de l\u2019amertume dans l\u2019\u00e2me, chacun \u00e0 cause de ses fils et de ses filles. Mais David reprit courage en s\u2019appuyant sur l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7","name":"1 Samuel 30:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5","name":"1 Samuel 30:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il dit au sacrificateur Abiathar, fils d\u2019Achim\u00e9lec: Apporte-moi donc l\u2019\u00e9phod! Abiathar apporta l\u2019\u00e9phod \u00e0 David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8","name":"1 Samuel 30:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6","name":"1 Samuel 30:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et David consulta l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en disant: Poursuivrai-je cette troupe? L\u2019atteindrai-je? L\u2019\u00c9ternel lui r\u00e9pondit: Poursuis, car tu atteindras, et tu d\u00e9livreras.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9","name":"1 Samuel 30:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7","name":"1 Samuel 30:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et David se mit en marche, lui et les six cents hommes qui \u00e9taient avec lui. Ils arriv\u00e8rent au torrent de Besor, o\u00f9 s\u2019arr\u00eat\u00e8rent ceux qui restaient en arri\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10","name":"1 Samuel 30:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8","name":"1 Samuel 30:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>David continua la poursuite avec quatre cents hommes; deux cents hommes s\u2019arr\u00eat\u00e8rent, trop fatigu\u00e9s pour passer le torrent de Besor.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11","name":"1 Samuel 30:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9","name":"1 Samuel 30:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ils trouv\u00e8rent dans les champs un homme \u00e9gyptien, qu\u2019ils conduisirent aupr\u00e8s de David. Ils lui firent manger du pain et boire de l\u2019eau,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12","name":"1 Samuel 30:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10","name":"1 Samuel 30:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>et ils lui donn\u00e8rent un morceau d\u2019une masse de figues s\u00e8ches et deux masses de raisins secs. Apr\u00e8s qu\u2019il eut mang\u00e9, les forces lui revinrent, car il n\u2019avait point pris de nourriture et point bu d\u2019eau depuis trois jours et trois nuits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13","name":"1 Samuel 30:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11","name":"1 Samuel 30:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>David lui dit: A qui es-tu, et d\u2019o\u00f9 es-tu? Il r\u00e9pondit: Je suis un gar\u00e7on \u00e9gyptien, au service d\u2019un homme amal\u00e9cite, et voil\u00e0 trois jours que mon ma\u00eetre m\u2019a abandonn\u00e9 parce que j\u2019\u00e9tais malade.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14","name":"1 Samuel 30:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12","name":"1 Samuel 30:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Nous avons fait une invasion dans le midi des K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens, sur le territoire de Juda et au midi de Caleb, et nous avons br\u00fbl\u00e9 Tsiklag.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15","name":"1 Samuel 30:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13","name":"1 Samuel 30:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>David lui dit: Veux-tu me faire descendre vers cette troupe? Et il r\u00e9pondit: Jure-moi par le nom de Dieu que tu ne me tueras pas et que tu ne me livreras pas \u00e0 mon ma\u00eetre, et je te ferai descendre vers cette troupe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16","name":"1 Samuel 30:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14","name":"1 Samuel 30:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:16","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il lui servit ainsi de guide. Et voici, les Amal\u00e9cites \u00e9taient r\u00e9pandus sur toute la contr\u00e9e, mangeant, buvant et dansant, \u00e0 cause du grand butin qu\u2019ils avaient enlev\u00e9 du pays des Philistins et du pays de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17","name":"1 Samuel 30:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15","name":"1 Samuel 30:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:17","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>David les battit depuis l\u2019aube du jour jusqu\u2019au soir du lendemain, et aucun d\u2019eux n\u2019\u00e9chappa, except\u00e9 quatre cents jeunes hommes qui mont\u00e8rent sur des chameaux et s\u2019enfuirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18","name":"1 Samuel 30:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16","name":"1 Samuel 30:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:18","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>David sauva tout ce que les Amal\u00e9cites avaient pris, et il d\u00e9livra aussi ses deux femmes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19","name":"1 Samuel 30:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17","name":"1 Samuel 30:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:19","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Il ne leur manqua personne, ni petit ni grand, ni fils ni fille, ni aucune chose du butin, ni rien de ce qu\u2019on leur avait enlev\u00e9: David ramena tout.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20","name":"1 Samuel 30:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18","name":"1 Samuel 30:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:20","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Et David prit tout le menu et le gros b\u00e9tail; et ceux qui conduisaient ce troupeau et marchaient \u00e0 sa t\u00eate disaient: C\u2019est ici le butin de David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21","name":"1 Samuel 30:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19","name":"1 Samuel 30:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:21","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>David arriva aupr\u00e8s des deux cents hommes qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 trop fatigu\u00e9s pour le suivre, et qu\u2019on avait laiss\u00e9s au torrent de Besor. Ils s\u2019avanc\u00e8rent \u00e0 la rencontre de David et du peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui. David s\u2019approcha d\u2019eux, et leur demanda comment ils se trouvaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22","name":"1 Samuel 30:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20","name":"1 Samuel 30:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:22","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Tous les hommes m\u00e9chants et vils parmi les gens qui \u00e9taient all\u00e9s avec David prirent la parole et dirent: Puisqu\u2019ils ne sont pas venus avec nous, nous ne leur donnerons rien du butin que nous avons sauv\u00e9, sinon \u00e0 chacun sa femme et ses enfants; qu\u2019ils les emm\u00e8nent, et s\u2019en aillent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23","name":"1 Samuel 30:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21","name":"1 Samuel 30:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:23","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Mais David dit: N\u2019agissez pas ainsi, mes fr\u00e8res, au sujet de ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel nous a donn\u00e9; car il nous a gard\u00e9s, et il a livr\u00e9 entre nos mains la troupe qui \u00e9tait venue contre nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24","name":"1 Samuel 30:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22","name":"1 Samuel 30:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:24","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Et qui vous \u00e9couterait dans cette affaire? La part doit \u00eatre la m\u00eame pour celui qui est descendu sur le champ de bataille et pour celui qui est rest\u00e9 pr\u00e8s des bagages: ensemble ils partageront.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25","name":"1 Samuel 30:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23","name":"1 Samuel 30:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:25","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il en fut ainsi d\u00e8s ce jour et dans la suite, et l\u2019on a fait de cela jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour une loi et une coutume en Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26","name":"1 Samuel 30:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24","name":"1 Samuel 30:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:26","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>De retour \u00e0 Tsiklag, David envoya une partie du butin aux anciens de Juda, \u00e0 ses amis, en leur adressant ces paroles: Voici pour vous un pr\u00e9sent sur le butin des ennemis de l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27","name":"1 Samuel 30:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25","name":"1 Samuel 30:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:27","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il fit ainsi des envois \u00e0 ceux de B\u00e9thel, \u00e0 ceux de Ramoth du midi, \u00e0 ceux de Jatthir,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28","name":"1 Samuel 30:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26","name":"1 Samuel 30:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:28","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>\u00e0 ceux d\u2019Aro\u00ebr, \u00e0 ceux de Siphmoth, \u00e0 ceux d\u2019Eschthemoa,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29","name":"1 Samuel 30:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27","name":"1 Samuel 30:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:29","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>\u00e0 ceux de Racal, \u00e0 ceux des villes des Jerachme\u00e9lites, \u00e0 ceux des villes des K\u00e9niens,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30","name":"1 Samuel 30:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28","name":"1 Samuel 30:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:30","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.030.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>\u00e0 ceux de Horma, \u00e0 ceux de Cor-Aschan, \u00e0 ceux d\u2019Athac,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.31","name":"1 Samuel 30:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29","name":"1 Samuel 30:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.31","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 30:31","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.030.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.031.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.30.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>\u00e0 ceux d\u2019H\u00e9bron, et dans tous les lieux que David et ses gens avaient parcourus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30","name":"1 Samuel 30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.31.1","name":"1 Samuel 31:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.31.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30","name":"1 Samuel 30:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.30.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/includ